<L>The fierce&s;t once, now broken with de&s;pair.</L>
<L>His tru&s;t was with great <HI>I&s;aac</HI> to be deem'd</L>
<L><PB N="78" REF="85">
A match in &s;trength, and rather than be le&s;s,</L>
<L>Car'd not to be at all. Grown humbler now,</L>
<L>As one, he &s;tood, e&s;cap'd from cruel fight,</L>
