</LG>
<LG>
<L><HI>O Prince, O Chief of many wronghead Powers,</HI></L>
<L><HI>That led th' imbattled</HI> Increments <HI>to War</HI></L>
<L><HI>Under thy conduct, and with dreadful blunders,</HI></L>
<L><HI>Brainle&s;s, endanger'd</HI> Newton<HI>'s deathle&s;s Fame</HI>;</L>
